Package coding201.gui

package coding201.gui
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AthleteDisplay
    athleteDisplay This extension of JPanel is used throughout the game to visually represent an athlete and their stats.
    ClubSetup
    clubSetup This method is responsible for setting up the club page.
    FinishPanel
    FinishPanel This is the finishing screen panel created after either all the weeks have finished, the user want's to quit the game or they cannot afford a new player.
    HomePanel
    HomePanel This is the main panel of the program, created after the club setup has been done.
    ItemDisplay
    ItemDisplay This extension of JPanel is what is used in the store and the TeamViewPanel in order to see a visual representation of purchaseableItem.
    MainFrame
    mainFrame This extension of JFrame is the main window in which the game runs.
    MatchRunner
    matchRunner This class is where the matches are simulated.
    StadiumPanel
    StadiumPanel StadiumPanel is the JPanel which allows the user to select an opposition team and begin a match.
    StorePanel
    StorePanel StorePanel is the JPanel where the store can be accessed.
    TeamViewPanel
    TeamViewPanel The TeamViewPanel is the JPanel from which all intra-team actions can take place.
